      <p class="section-description">
        Ecommerce platforms have made shopping easier and more convenient, allowing people to buy and sell products online. Many platforms serve different types of customers, including businesses and individuals. Below are five major eCommerce platforms, along with some examples of other platforms.
      </p>

      <!-- Platform List -->
      <div class="platform-list">
        <!-- Amazon -->
        <div class="platform-item">
          <img src="https://m.media-amazon.com/images/I/31i63XNCykL.jpg" alt="Amazon Logo" class="platform-logo">
          <div class="platform-content">
            <h3>Amazon</h3>
            <p>Amazon is one of the largest online shopping platforms in the world. Founded in 1994 by Jeff Bezos, it offers a wide range of products, including electronics, clothing, books, and groceries. Amazon provides fast delivery services like Amazon Prime and allows both businesses and individuals to sell products on its marketplace.</p>
            <a href="https://www.amazon.com" target="_blank">Visit Amazon</a>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Flipkart -->
        <div class="platform-item">
          <img src="https://media.licdn.com/dms/image/v2/D560BAQEb2s2nxdNpXQ/company-logo_200_200/B56ZUT2sHrGoAM-/0/1739794858896/flipkart_logo?e=2147483647&v=beta&t=tMYbxj27etFIkemuKPVUSFb7HGl94cb6kkNxnHlMtW4" alt="Flipkart Logo" class="platform-logo">
          <div class="platform-content">
            <h3>Flipkart</h3>
            <p>Flipkart is a leading eCommerce platform in India. Launched in 2007, it sells various products like fashion, electronics, and home essentials. Known for offering discounts and special sales events, Flipkart is a favorite among Indian shoppers. In 2018, Walmart acquired Flipkart, strengthening its presence in the Indian market.</p>
            <a href="https://www.flipkart.com" target="_blank">Visit Flipkart</a>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Daraz -->
        <div class="platform-item">
          <img src="https://encrypted-tbn0.gstatic.com/images?q=tbn:ANd9GcRwL6BFy1WfOFyvroC4Ukr1NHXbbsSL3_dgxg&s" alt="Daraz Logo" class="platform-logo">
          <div class="platform-content">
            <h3>Daraz</h3>
            <p>Daraz is a popular online shopping platform in South Asia, including Nepal, Pakistan, Bangladesh, and Sri Lanka. It was founded in 2012 and provides a marketplace where businesses and individuals can sell products. Daraz offers many discounts and provides fast delivery services in local markets.</p>
            <a href="https://www.daraz.com" target="_blank">Visit Daraz</a>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Alibaba -->
        <div class="platform-item">
          <img src="https://encrypted-tbn0.gstatic.com/images?q=tbn:ANd9GcRjsCwkZ1jOlAPCMYnW34riRLR40koItso-vw&s" alt="Alibaba Logo" class="platform-logo">
          <div class="platform-content">
            <h3>Alibaba</h3>
            <p>Alibaba is a Chinese eCommerce platform focused on business-to-business (B2B) sales. Founded by Jack Ma in 1999, it helps businesses buy wholesale products directly from manufacturers. Alibaba also owns platforms like AliExpress, which allows people to buy products in small quantities at affordable prices.</p>
            <a href="https://www.alibaba.com" target="_blank">Visit Alibaba</a>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- SastoDeal -->
        <div class="platform-item">
          <img src="https://encrypted-tbn0.gstatic.com/images?q=tbn:ANd9GcSVmqm2aUpkOtfzkYTRMHpPUemTqFv3FEKTcg&s" alt="SastoDeal Logo" class="platform-logo">
          <div class="platform-content">
            <h3>SastoDeal</h3>
            <p>SastoDeal is one of Nepal’s leading eCommerce platforms. It offers a wide variety of products, including electronics, fashion, and home appliances. SastoDeal partners with local and international brands to provide customers with high-quality products at competitive prices.</p>
            <a href="https://www.sastodeal.com" target="_blank">Visit SastoDeal</a>
          </div>
