      <!-- Other Platforms Section -->
      <div class="other-platforms">
        <h3>Other eCommerce Platforms</h3>
        <p>In addition to these five, many other platforms are popular in different regions:</p>
        <ul>
          <li><a href="https://www.ebay.com" target="_blank">eBay</a> – A global marketplace known for auctions and second-hand products.</li>
          <li><a href="https://www.walmart.com" target="_blank">Walmart</a> – A retail giant with a strong online presence.</li>
          <li><a href="https://www.shopify.com" target="_blank">Shopify</a> – A platform that helps businesses create their own online stores.</li>
          <li><a href="https://www.aliexpress.com" target="_blank">AliExpress</a> – A Chinese marketplace offering affordable products worldwide.</li>
          <li><a href="https://www.myntra.com" target="_blank">Myntra</a> – A fashion-focused eCommerce platform in India.</li>
          <li><a href="https://www.hamrobazar.com" target="_blank">HamroBazar</a> – A popular Nepali online classifieds platform for buying and selling goods.</li>
        </ul>
        <p>eCommerce continues to grow, making shopping easier and more accessible worldwide. New platforms and technologies keep improving the online shopping experience for both businesses and customers.</p>
